divs: Sighting DetailsThe sky at sunset was a really pretty color, as you can see in the photo. I got my camera and from my backyard, facing south, I took some photos. It wasn't until I had downloaded them to my computer that I saw the 2 objects the camera had caught. I didn't even know they were there when I took the photo, so there's only this one, but it was pretty amazing.
